data.description:
Located on a beautiful .81acre property, this three-bedroom, two-bath home features an open style living, dining, kitchen area with views to a very expansive backyard.  Trayed ceilings in the Primary Bedroom and Den. 18 feet x 26 feet detached garage with 10-foot door is perfect for one car plus hobbies and toys. Lot opens up at the rear with views of large pond. This well-designed home with .81 acres is conveniently close to local shopping and restaurants.
ON LOCKBOX AND EASY TO SHOW !!!!!
